  "text": "The same conclusion is drawn in [CITATION_1] by analyzing the E dyn total variability of the static CMOS S-box at low voltages where it is dominated by the WID α F variability. It is worth mentioning that the D2D α F variability is far less important in this case as measurements are done on the same wafer. Min.",
